This is a fix of fy_poolparty_v2, there were some annoying things and i also think that the map is not perfectly balanced.

I removed the black bar over the ct spawn and also the gap where the t's could camp. I made a func_illusionary glass at t spawn where ct's could see t's feet, you can go, but don't shoot through. There are also some other small fixes and changes...

I didn't make a rush protection, because there are server scripts which work better.

pls test and leave a comment, its my first upload ;)

lg eatthefish
